.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
2 different games are played: chess, billiard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, parkour
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person playing chess##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| Game           | billiard | chess     |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | r&b         |
| Sport     | parkour         | badminton   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, fuchsia
2 different pets are kept: hamster, rat
1. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Birthday      | july     | march   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | action |
| Color   | orange   | fuchsia |
| Pet           | hamster | rat    |

