There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower
2 different pets are kept: bird, pony
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | milk     | iced-tea |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Flower   | sunflower     | amaryllis     |
| Pet     | bird | pony     |

 